  "date": "2026-02-10",
  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">Corruption Risk Mapping<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Interview minutes<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"699\" style=\"width:524.1pt;\n mso-cellspacing:1.5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:110.75pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Item</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"545\" style=\"width:408.85pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Information</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:110.75pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interview\n  date</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"545\" style=\"width:408.85pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">February 10, 2026<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:110.75pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewee</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"545\" style=\"width:408.85pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Jaime CASTILLO<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:110.75pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Position</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"545\" style=\"width:408.85pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Commercial Director – LFB Mexico<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:110.75pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewers</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"545\" style=\"width:408.85pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Sandra Lasagni, Antoine Lassauge<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0\">1. Responsibilities and\nActivities<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"ES\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:ES\">Commercial\n     Director for LFB Mexico</span></b><span lang=\"ES\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:ES\">.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Responsible for: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Oversight\n      of the <b>commercial team (7 sales representatives</b>).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Management\n      of relationships with <b>public and private healthcare institutions</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Coordination\n      of participation in the <b>national public tender</b> (every 2 years).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Supervision\n      of <b>distributors</b> (10 currently) to private and public market.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Responsibility\n      for <b>Marketing</b> and <b>Supply Chain</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\npage-break-after:avoid\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%;color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2. Third Parties, Interactions,\nRisks &amp; Controls<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\npage-break-after:avoid\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">A. Public Institutions<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Main institutions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">IMSS:\n      Mexican&nbsp;Institute&nbsp;of&nbsp;Social&nbsp;Security<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">ISTE:\n      Health Institution for employees of the public and government offices<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">IMS Bienestar:\n      Institution for people without social security (~50% of the population)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Army/Navy<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Normally,\n      70% of sales come from fibrinogen and 30% from IG (today no IG).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Tender\n      submission and follow-up:<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">A <b>single\n       consolidated public tender every 2 years</b> covering all national\n       institutions (LFB Mexico currently preparing documents for the 2027-2028\n       tender).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Entire\n       process is <b>online</b>, no face-to-face interactions with authorities\n       allowed before selection.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Online\n       platform for all documents.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">One\n       institution has several hospitals around the country (e.g., ~600\n       hospital for IMSS) – no decision is made by hospitals, decision-making\n       is with institutions (contracts are signed with institutions and not\n       with hospitals).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Post-award\n      meetings limited to demand and supply topics — never pricing.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Potential\n      for <b>regional institutions to impose a distributor</b> not authorized\n      by LFB / Risk of <b>favoritism toward certain distributors</b> chosen by\n      public officials – Risk that prices are not at FMV in this situation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Participation\n      to the public tenders is a risk area but no ability to influence the\n      tender due to fully digital process.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\nmargin-left:35.7pt;text-indent:-17.85pt;page-break-after:avoid;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4;\ntab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Existing controls</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\n      auto;page-break-after:avoid;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo4;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">100% digital tender process.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No pre‑tender\n      physical contact possible.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Post tender\n      meetings always conducted with <b>at least 2 LFB participants (“4 eyes\n      review”)</b> including General Manager and Government Sales Manager. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Clear\n      separation between price and operational discussions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Distributors\n      must be authorized by LFB Mexico even if imposed by institutions – LFB\n      Mexico already lost business because the distributor was not authorized.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Good\n      process to control the risk of conflict of interest.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">B. Healthcare Professionals (HCPs)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Daily\n      interactions</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> with physicians. Minimum\n      interactions with nurses or pharmacists (role of a pharmacist in Mexico\n      very different from the role of a pharmacist in Europe or in the US –\n      rather low profile).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Promotion</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:\n      EN-US\"> of LFB products strictly <b>limited to</b> <b>technical</b> and <b>scientific</b>\n      aspects of products - <b>No discussion of pricing</b> with HCPs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Occasional\n      professional meals (rather breakfasts than dinners).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Congress\n      invitations - <b>Limited sponsorship of HCPs</b> (up to 100 HCPs/year).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Sometimes\n      booths at a congress (depending on budget).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Requests\n      for <b>letters from physicians</b> to support <b>inclusion of new\n      products</b> (ex. Cevenfact<b>) in the government catalogue</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      undue advantage (meals, sponsorship) in exchange for influence or product\n      endorsement.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk\n      related to travel sponsorship for congresses.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">€40 per\n      person limit</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> for meals.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Business\n      appropriate locations; alcohol prohibited.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Always <b>“four‑eyes” presence</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Strict\n      rules for congress sponsorship: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Letter from HCP</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> required.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Only\n       registration, flights, and hotel covered and sometimes, inclusion of a\n       dinner<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Stay\n       strictly <b>limited to congress dates</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">KOL\n      engagement managed by Medical Affairs (but influenced by commercials as\n      they generally propose new KOLs).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">C. Distributors<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Negotiation\n      of logistic conditions and prices - 10 distributors used, purely for <b>logistics</b>\n      (no promotion allowed in Mexico).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Visits to distributor premises.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk\n      that an institution might <b>force the use of a non‑authorized\n      distributor</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      corruption <b>originating from the distributor</b> to secure a contract.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      misaligned pricing or margin structures.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\nmargin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-17.85pt;page-break-after:avoid;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo3;\ntab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\nmargin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-17.85pt;page-break-after:avoid;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo3;\ntab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Tender rules prohibit distributor\nparticipation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Mandatory\n      background checks (financial + compliance) of distributor performed by\n      Finance.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Visit\n      on-site to meet with each distributor.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Selection\n      follows a strict, multi departmental approval process: collective\n      decision-making (Commercial + Finance + General Manager).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Formal\n      written contracts required for all distributors.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Background\n      checks, contract signature and purchase orders systematically reviewed by\n      the client services person.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">“Four‑eyes”\n      rule for all negotiations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\npage-break-after:avoid\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">D. Agencies and External Service Providers<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Selection\n      controlled by Purchasing: 3-4 agencies used.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Marketing\n      materials, visual aids, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Low\n      risk.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Purchasing\n      procedure with at least 3 offers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Final decision by Procurement.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">E.\nInternal stakeholders – Sales Representatives<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Compensation &amp; incentives</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">70% fixed salary / 30% bonus.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">30%-bonus split: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">50% collective target<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">50%\n       individual target (based on available sales data from an external\n       supplier – with some institutions only because of limited visibility on\n       sales done by each sales representative).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No risk\n      mentioned regarding potential incentive driven misconduct.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Bonus\n      program always presented to headquarters.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Bonus\n      calculation performed by the Salesforce Effectiveness Manager\n      (independent from Sales – direct report to GM).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Triple\n      validation of bonuses: Commercial Director, Finance, General Manager.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Limited\n      access to complete sales data (sell‑out), reducing manipulation risk.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">F.\nSuggestions for additional compliance guidance<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Practical\n     training specific to interactions with public procurement.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Guidance\n     regarding interactions with distributors.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Standardized\n     compliance checklist for customer visits, especially in the public sector.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Templates\n     or guidance for communication during the tender process.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>",
